ont-black font-heading mb-6\" data-kid=\"213\">Как это работает</h2>\n      <p class=\"text-white/40 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"214\">Простой путь от новичка до профессионала за 5 четко выверенных шагов.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 relative\" data-kid=\"215\">\n      \n      <div class=\"absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-white/10 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"216\">\n        <div class=\"w-full h-full bg-cyan-500/50 timeline-progress-bar scale-y-0 origin-top\" data-kid=\"217\"></div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"space-y-32\" data-kid=\"218\">\n        \n        <div class=\"relative grid grid-cols-12 items-center timeline-step\" data-kid=\"219\">\n          <div class=\"col-span-5 text-right pr-16\" data-kid=\"220\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-4 font-heading\" data-kid=\"221\">Погружение</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-white/40 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"222\">Знакомство с профессией и рынком грузоперевозок США. Основные термины и правила безопасности.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-span-2 flex justify-center relative z-10\" data-kid=\"223\">\n            <div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-bg-dark border-4 border-cyan-500/30 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-cyan-400\" data-kid=\"224\">1</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-span-5 pl-16\" data-kid=\"225\">\n             <div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-cyan-500/40 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"226\">Phase 01</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"relative grid grid-cols-12 items-center timeline-step\" data-kid=\"227\">\n          <div class=\"col-span-5 text-right pr-16\" data-kid=\"228\">\n            <div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-500/40 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"229\">Phase 02</div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"col-span-2 flex justify-center relative z-10\" data-kid=\"230\">\n