      <i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-purple-500\" data-kid=\"299\"></i>\n            Персональные занятия\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-white/60 text-sm\" data-kid=\"300\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-purple-500\" data-kid=\"301\"></i>\n            Помощь в трудоустройстве\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n        <button class=\"w-full py-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 font-bold hover:bg-white/5 transition-all\" data-kid=\"302\">Выбрать</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-32 relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"303\">\n    \n    <div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] cta-glow\" data-kid=\"304\"></div>\n    \n    <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"305\">\n      <div class=\"glass-panel p-20 text-center border-white/10\" data-kid=\"306\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-6xl font-black font-heading mb-8 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"307\">Готовы начать карьеру <br data-kid=\"308\"> <span class=\"text-cyan-400 tracking-tight italic\" data-kid=\"309\">Диспетчера?</span></h2>\n        <p class=\"text-white/50 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-16\" data-kid=\"310\">\n          Присоединяйтесь к закрытому комьюнити профессионалов. Получите доступ ко всем материалам, AI-симулятору и поддержке менторов 24/7.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"flex justify-center gap-8\" data-kid=\"311\">\n           <button class=\"px-12 py-5 bg-cyan-500 text-black rounded-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-2xl shadow-cyan-500/20\" data-kid=\"312\">Начать бесплатно</button>\n           <button class=\"px-12 py-5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white/5 transition-all\" data-kid=\"313\">Связаться с нами</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mt-16 flex justify-center items-center gap-8 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/20\" data-kid=\"314\">\n          <span data-kid=\"315\">Lifetime Access</span>\n          <div class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-white/20\" data-kid=\"316\"></div>\n          <span data-kid=\"317\">Monthly Updates</span>\n          <div class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-white/20\" data-kid=\"318\"></div>\n          <span data-kid=\"319\">Mentor Support</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</main>\n\n<footer class=\"py-20 border-t border-white/5 bg-bg-darker\" data-kid=\"320\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-12\" data-kid=\"321\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-xs\" data-kid=\"322\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\" data-kid=\"323\">\n        <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-cyan-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\" data-kid=\"324\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-truck-delivery text-black text-sm\" data-kid=\"325\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"text-lg font-bold font-heading uppercase tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"326\">Dispatch4You</span>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"text-sm text-white/40 leading-relaxed mb-8\" data-kid=\"327\">Элитная академия диспетчеров грузоперевозок США. Обучение с нулевого уровня до профи.</p>\n      <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"328\">\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-cyan-500 hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"329\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-brand-facebook\" data-kid=\"330\"></i>\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-cyan-500 hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"331\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-brand-instagram\" data-kid=\"332\"></i>\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-cyan-500 hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"333\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-brand-telegram\" data-kid=\"334\"></i>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16\" data-kid=\"335\">\n      <div data-kid=\"336\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-6\" data-kid=\"337\">Продукт</h4>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/40\" data-kid=\"338\">\n          <li data-kid=\"339\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"340\">Курс</a></li>\n          <li data-kid=\"341\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"342\">Тренажер</a></li>\n          <li data-kid=\"343\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"344\">AI Бот</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div data-kid=\"345\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-6\" data-kid=\"346\">Компания</h4>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/40\" data-kid=\"347\">\n          <li data-kid=\"348\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"349\">О нас</a></li>\n          <li data-kid=\"350\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"351\">Отзывы</a></li>\n          <li data-kid=\"352\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"353\">Контакты</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n      <div data-kid=\"354\">\n        <h4 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-6\" data-kid=\"355\">Право</h4>\n        <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/40\" data-kid=\"356\">\n          <li data-kid=\"357\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"358\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n          <li data-kid=\"359\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"360\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-12 mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 text-[10px] font-bold text-white/20 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"361\">\n    © 2026 Dispatch4You Training Academy. All rights reserved.\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"362\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"363\"></script>\n\n<script data-kid=\"364\">\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n  window.addEventListener('load', () => {\n    // Hero Entrance\n    const tl = gsap.timeline();\n    tl.from('.hero-reveal h1', { y: 100, opacity: 0, duration: 1.2, ease: 'power4.out' })\n      .from('.hero-reveal p', { y: 30, opacity: 0, duration: 1, ease: 'power3.out' }, '-=0.8')\n      .from('.hero-reveal .flex', { y: 20, opacity: 0, duration: 0.8, ease: 'power3.out' }, '-=0.6')\n      .from('.hero-reveal .mt-20', { opacity: 0, duration: 1 }, '-=0.4');\n\n    // Bento Grid Reveal\n    gsap.from('.bento-reveal .group', {\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: '.bento-reveal',\n        start: 'top 80%',\n      },\n      y: 60,\n      opacity: 0,\n      stagger: 0.1,\n      duration: 1,\n      ease: 'power3.out'\n    });\n\n    // Parallax Map\n    gsap.to('.parallax-bg', {\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: '.parallax-bg',\n        start: 'top bottom',\n        end: 'bottom top',\n        scrub: true\n      },\n      yPercent: 15,\n      ease: 'none'\n    });\n\n    // Timeline Progress\n    gsap.to('.timeline-progress-bar', {\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: '.timeline-progress-bar',\n        start: 'top 60%',\n        end: 'bottom 40%',\n        scrub: true\n      },\n      scaleY: 1,\n      ease: 'none'\n    });\n\n    // Fade in sections\n    gsap.utils.toArray('section').forEach(section => {\n      gsap.from(section.querySelectorAll('h2, p'), {\n        scrollTrigger: {\n          trigger: section,\n          start: 'top 85%',\n        },\n        y: 30,\n        opacity: 0,\n        stagger: 0.1,\n        duration: 0.8\n      });\n    });\n\n    // CTA Glow Animation\n    gsap.to('.cta-glow', {\n      scale: 1.2,\n      opacity: 0.2,\n      duration: 5,\n      repeat: -1,\n      yoyo: true,\n      ease: 'sine.inOut'\n    });\n  });\n</script>",
