-t from-(--bg-dark) to-transparent\" data-kid=\"73\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      \n      <div class=\"glass p-10 rounded-2xl group hover:border-(--primary)/30 transition-all reveal\" data-kid=\"74\">\n        <i class=\"ti ti-headset text-4xl text-(--primary) mb-6 block\" data-kid=\"75\"></i>\n        <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\" data-kid=\"76\">24/7 Менторская поддержка</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"77\">Действующие диспетчеры отвечают на ваши вопросы в закрытом чате. Среднее время ответа — 15 минут.</p>\n        <span class=\"px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-[10px] font-bold text-white/40 uppercase\" data-kid=\"78\">Elite Support</span>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"glass p-10 rounded-2xl group hover:border-(--primary)/30 transition-all reveal\" data-kid=\"79\">\n        <i class=\"ti ti-trending-up text-4xl text-(--accent) mb-6 block\" data-kid=\"80\"></i>\n        <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\" data-kid=\"81\">Карьерный рост</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"82\">Помощь с резюме, подготовка к собеседованию и доступ к эксклюзивной базе вакансий.</p>\n        <div class=\"text-(--accent) font-bold text-xl\" data-kid=\"83\">87% трудоустроены</div>\n      </div>\n\n      \n      <div class=\"glass p-10 rounded-2xl md:col-span-2 group hover:border-(--primary)/30 transition-all reveal\" data-kid=\"84\">\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-10 items-center\" data-kid=\"85\">\n          <div class=\"flex-1\" data-kid=\"86\">\n            <span class=\"text-(--secondary) text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block\" data-kid=\"87\">Academy Hub</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-4\" data-kid=\"88\">Полная база знаний</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"89\">Доступ ко всем типам документов: Rate Con, BOL, POD, Invoice. Интерактивные шаблоны и актуальные чек-листы 2026 года.</p>\n            <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"90\">\n               <div class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"91\">15+ ТИПОВ DOCS</div>\n               <div class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded text-[10px] font-bold\" data-kid=\"92\">PDF ШАБЛОНЫ</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"w-full md:w-64 h-48 bg-(--bg-dark) rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5 relative\" data-kid=\"93\">\n             <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/5831260/pexels-photo-5831260.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Knowledge\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\" data-kid=\"94\">\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-(--bg-dark) to-transparent\" data-kid=\"95\"></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section id=\"features\" class=\"py-32 bg-(--bg-dark)\" data-kid=\"96\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-8 mb-16\" data-kid=\"97\">\n     <div class=\"flex justify-between items-end\" data-kid=\"98\">\n       <div data-kid=\"99\">\n         <h2 class=\"text-4xl font-black font-montserrat uppercase mb-2\" data-kid=\"100\">Инструменты <span class=\"text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"101\">успеха</span></h2>\n         <p class=\"text-white/40 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs\" data-kid=\"102\">Все необходимое в одном месте</p>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"flex gap-4\" data-kid=\"103\">\n         <button class=\"w-12 h-12 border border-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-(--primary) hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"104\"><i class=\"ti ti-chevron-left\" data-kid=\"105\"></i></button>\n         <button class=\"w-12 h-12 border border-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-(--primary) hover:text-bla