 items-center gap-2 mt-8 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all\" data-kid=\"139\">Программа <i class=\"ti ti-arrow-right\" data-kid=\"140\"></i></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"relative py-48 overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"141\">\n  <video src=\"https://videos.pexels.com/video-files/3129785/3129785-uhd_2560_1440_25fps.mp4\" autoplay muted loop playsinline class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0\" poster=\"https://images.pexels.com/videos/3129785/free-video-3129785.jpg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&fit=crop&h=630&w=1200\" data-kid=\"142\"></video>\n  <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-(--bg-darker) via-(--bg-darker)/80 to-transparent z-10\" data-kid=\"143\"></div>\n  \n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-8 relative z-20\" data-kid=\"144\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-2xl reveal\" data-kid=\"145\">\n      <span class=\"px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-(--primary) text-black text-[10px] font-black uppercase mb-6 inline-block\" data-kid=\"146\">Interactive Training</span>\n      <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-black font-montserrat uppercase mb-6 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"147\">Интерактивный<br data-kid=\"148\"><span class=\"text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"149\">Тренажер Карт</span></h2>\n      <p class=\"text-xl text-white/70 mb-10 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"150\">\n        Освойте географию США и логистические хабы в игровом формате. Знание штатов и часовых поясов — залог эффективного планирования.\n      </p>\n      <a href=\"/map-trainer/\" class=\"px-10 py-4 border border-(--primary) text-(--primary) font-bold rounded-sm uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-(--primary) hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"151\">Запустить тренажер</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"py-32 relative\" data-kid=\"152\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"153\">\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center\" data-kid=\"154\">\n      <div class=\"reveal\" data-kid=\"155\">\n         <div class=\"mb-12\" data-kid=\"156\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-4xl font-black font-montserrat uppercase mb-6\" data-kid=\"157\">Профессия с <span class=\"text-(--accent)\" data-kid=\"158\">неограниченным</span> потенциалом</h2>\n            <p class=\"text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-lg\" data-kid=\"159\">Логистика — это фундамент экономики США. Диспетчеры всегда востребованы, независимо от сезона и экономической ситуации.</p>\n         </div>\n         \n         <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-8\" data-kid=\"160\">\n            <div class=\"p-8 glass rounded-2xl\" data-kid=\"161\">\n               <div class=\"text-4xl font-black text-(--primary) mb-2 counter\" data-target=\"875\" data-kid=\"162\">$875B</div>\n               <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"163\">Объем рынка в год</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"p-8 glass rounded-2xl\" data-kid=\"164\">\n               <div class=\"text-4xl font-black text-(--accent) mb-2 counter\" data-target=\"3.5\" data-kid=\"165\">3.5M+</div>\n               <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"166\">Активных траков</p>\n            </div>\n         </div>\n         \n         <div class=\"mt-12 space-y-6\" data-kid=\"167\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" data-kid=\"168\">\n               <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-(--primary)/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"169\"><i class=\"ti ti-coin text-2xl\" data-kid=\"170\"></i></div>\n               <div data-kid=\"171\">\n                  <h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\" data-kid=\"172\">Высокий доход в валюте</h4>\n                  <p class=\"text-white/50 text-sm\" data-kid=\"173\">Средний доход опытного диспетчера составляет от $5,000 до $12,000 в месяц.</p>\n               </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\" data-kid=\"174\">\n               <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-(--secondary)/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-(--secondary)\" data-kid=\"175\"><i class=\"ti ti-world text-2xl\" data-kid=\"176\"></i></div>\n               <div data-kid=\"177\">\n                  <h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg\" data-kid=\"178\">Удаленная свобода</h4>\n                  <p class=\"text-white/50 text-sm\" data-kid=\"179\">Работайте из любой точки мира — вам нужен только ноутбук и надежный интернет.</p>\n               </div>\n            </div>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"relative reveal\" data-kid=\"180\">\n         <div class=\"aspect-square rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5 shadow-2xl relative group\" data-kid=\"181\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581089781785-603411fa81e5?auto=format&w=800&q=80&fit=crop\" alt=\"Professional Dispatcher\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-50 group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-1000\" data-kid=\"182\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-(--bg-darker) via-transparent to-transparent\" data-kid=\"183\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"absolute top-10 right-10 glass p-6 rounded-2xl max-w-[200px] border-(--primary)/30\" data-kid=\"184\">\n               <div class=\"text-xs font-bold text-(--primary) uppercase tracking-widest mb-2\" data-kid=\"185\">System Status</div>\n               <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\" data-kid=\"186\">\n                  <span class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"187\"></span> NOMINAL / ACTIVE\n               </div>\n            </div>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section id=\"how\" class=\"py-32 bg-(--bg-darker)\" data-kid=\"188\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"189\">\n     <div class=\"text-center mb-32\" data-kid=\"190\">\n       <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-montserrat uppercase mb-4\" data-kid=\"191\">Ваш путь к <span class=\"text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"192\">вершине</span></h2>\n       <p class=\"text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold\" data-kid=\"193\">5 шагов до новой карьеры</p>\n     </div>\n     \n     <div class=\"relative max-w-4xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"194\">\n        <div class=\"timeline-wire\" data-kid=\"195\"></div>\n        <div class=\"timeline-fill\" id=\"timeline-fill\" data-kid=\"196\"></div>\n        \n        <div class=\"space-y-40 relative\" data-kid=\"197\">\n           \n           <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-0 timeline-node\" data-kid=\"198\">\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pr-20 md:text-right\" data-kid=\"199\">\n                 <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase\" data-kid=\"200\">Погружение</h4>\n                 <p class=\"text-white/50 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"201\">Основы рынка США, терминология, типы траков и юридические аспекты DOT/FMCSA.</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-(--bg-darker) border-2 border-(--primary) rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-(--primary) z-10 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)]\" data-kid=\"202\">1</div>\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pl-20\" data-kid=\"203\"></div>\n           </div>\n\n           \n           <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10 md:gap-0 timeline-node\" data-kid=\"204\">\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pl-20\" data-kid=\"205\">\n                 <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase\" data-kid=\"206\">Инструменты</h4>\n                 <p class=\"text-white/50 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"207\">Работа с Load Boards (DAT, Truckstop), чтение ставок и маршрутов, проверка брокеров.</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-(--bg-darker) border-2 border-(--primary) rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-(--primary) z-10 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)]\" data-kid=\"208\">2</div>\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pr-20\" data-kid=\"209\"></div>\n           </div>\n\n           \n           <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-0 timeline-node\" data-kid=\"210\">\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pr-20 md:text-right\" data-kid=\"211\">\n                 <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase\" data-kid=\"212\">Закрепление</h4>\n                 <p class=\"text-white/50 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"213\">Интерактивные тесты, квизы и флеш-карточки по каждому изученному модулю.</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-(--bg-darker) border-2 border-(--primary) rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-(--primary) z-10 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)]\" data-kid=\"214\">3</div>\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pl-20\" data-kid=\"215\"></div>\n           </div>\n\n           \n           <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10 md:gap-0 timeline-node\" data-kid=\"216\">\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pl-20\" data-kid=\"217\">\n                 <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase\" data-kid=\"218\">Практика</h4>\n                 <p class=\"text-white/50 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"219\">Переговоры в AI-симуляторе и разбор более 300+ реальных кейсов из практики профи.</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-(--bg-darker) border-2 border-(--primary) rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-(--primary) z-10 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)]\" data-kid=\"220\">4</div>\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pr-20\" data-kid=\"221\"></div>\n           </div>\n\n           \n           <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 md:gap-0 timeline-node\" data-kid=\"222\">\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pr-20 md:text-right\" data-kid=\"223\">\n                 <h4 class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase\" data-kid=\"224\">Старт карьеры</h4>\n                 <p class=\"text-white/50 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"225\">Подготовка резюме, имитация собеседований и выход на рынок труда США.</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-(--bg-darker) border-2 border-(--primary) rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-black text-(--primary) z-10 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)]\" data-kid=\"226\">5</div>\n              <div class=\"md:w-1/2 md:pl-20\" data-kid=\"227\"></div>\n           </div>\n        </div>\n     </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section id=\"pricing\" class=\"py-32 relative bg-(--bg-dark)\" data-kid=\"228\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"229\">\n     <div class=\"text-center mb-24\" data-kid=\"230\">\n       <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-montserrat uppercase mb-4\" data-kid=\"231\">Инвестируйте в <span class=\"text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"232\">будущее</span></h2>\n       <p class=\"text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-bold\" data-kid=\"233\">Прозрачные тарифы для любых целей</p>\n     </div>\n     \n     <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-stretch\" data-kid=\"234\">\n        \n        <div class=\"glass p-12 rounded-3xl flex flex-col justify-between border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 transition-all reveal\" data-kid=\"235\">\n           <div data-kid=\"236\">\n              <span class=\"text-white/40 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest block mb-8\" data-kid=\"237\">Starter</span>\n              <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-2\" data-kid=\"238\">Базовый</h3>\n              <div class=\"text-5xl font-black mb-10\" data-kid=\"239\">FREE</div>\n              <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/60 mb-12\" data-kid=\"240\">\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"241\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"242\"></i> 3 базовых модуля</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"243\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"244\"></i> Основная документация</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"245\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"246\"></i> Базовые тесты</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 opacity-30\" data-kid=\"247\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-x-filled\" data-kid=\"248\"></i> AI Симулятор</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3 opacity-30\" data-kid=\"249\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-x-filled\" data-kid=\"250\"></i> Менторская поддержка</li>\n              </ul>\n           </div>\n           <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-full py-4 border border-white/10 rounded-sm text-center font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"251\">Попробовать</a>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"rotating-border rounded-3xl reveal shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)]\" data-kid=\"252\">\n           <div class=\"rotating-border-inner rounded-3xl p-12 flex flex-col justify-between\" data-kid=\"253\">\n              <div data-kid=\"254\">\n                 <div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-8\" data-kid=\"255\">\n                    <span class=\"text-(--primary) text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest block\" data-kid=\"256\">Pro Choice</span>\n                    <span class=\"px-3 py-1 bg-(--primary)/10 text-(--primary) text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full border border-(--primary)/20 uppercase\" data-kid=\"257\">Most Popular</span>\n                 </div>\n                 <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-2\" data-kid=\"258\">Полный доступ</h3>\n                 <div class=\"text-5xl font-black mb-10 text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"259\">$1,000</div>\n                 <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/80 mb-12\" data-kid=\"260\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"261\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"262\"></i> Все 15 модулей курса</li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"263\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"264\"></i> AI Симулятор диспетчера</li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"265\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"266\"></i> 300+ реальных кейсов</li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"267\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"268\"></i> Групповые уроки еженедельно</li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"269\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"270\"></i> Поддержка 24/7</li>\n                 </ul>\n              </div>\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-full py-4 bg-(--primary) text-black rounded-sm text-center font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-(--secondary) transition-all\" data-kid=\"271\">Купить курс</a>\n           </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"glass p-12 rounded-3xl flex flex-col justify-between border-white/5 hover:border-white/10 transition-all reveal\" data-kid=\"272\">\n           <div data-kid=\"273\">\n              <span class=\"text-white/40 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest block mb-8\" data-kid=\"274\">Enterprise</span>\n              <h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-2\" data-kid=\"275\">Премиум</h3>\n              <div class=\"text-5xl font-black mb-10\" data-kid=\"276\">$1,750</div>\n              <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/60 mb-12\" data-kid=\"277\">\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"278\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--secondary)\" data-kid=\"279\"></i> Всё из Полного доступа</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"280\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--secondary)\" data-kid=\"281\"></i> Личный ментор 24/7</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"282\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--secondary)\" data-kid=\"283\"></i> Помощь в трудоустройстве</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"284\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--secondary)\" data-kid=\"285\"></i> Закрытое комьюнити профи</li>\n                 <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"286\"><i class=\"ti ti-circle-check-filled text-(--secondary)\" data-kid=\"287\"></i> Приоритетная поддержка</li>\n              </ul>\n           </div>\n           <a href=\"#\" class=\"w-full py-4 border border-white/10 rounded-sm text-center font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"288\">Выбрать Премиум</a>\n        </div>\n     </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"py-32 relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"289\">\n  <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1637139927081-14f741237e72?auto=format&w=1440&q=80\" alt=\"Fleet\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0 opacity-20 grayscale\" data-kid=\"290\">\n  <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-(--bg-darker) via-(--bg-darker)/80 to-(--bg-darker) z-10\" data-kid=\"291\"></div>\n  \n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-8 relative z-20 text-center\" data-kid=\"292\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto reveal\" data-kid=\"293\">\n       <span class=\"px-6 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-(--primary) mb-10 inline-block\" data-kid=\"294\">Ready to Start?</span>\n       <h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black font-montserrat uppercase mb-8 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"295\">ГОТОВЫ НАЧАТЬ КАРЬЕРУ<br data-kid=\"296\"><span class=\"text-(--primary)\" data-kid=\"297\">ДИСПЕТЧЕРА</span> СЕГОДНЯ?</h2>\n       <p class=\"text-xl text-white/50 mb-16 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"298\">\n         Присоединяйтесь к 500+ успешным студентам. Начните обучение сейчас и выйдите на доход от $3,000 уже через несколько месяцев.\n       </p>\n       \n       <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-20\" data-kid=\"299\">\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"300\">\n             <span class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-2\" data-kid=\"301\">500+</span>\n             <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"302\">Учеников</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center border-x border-white/10\" data-kid=\"303\">\n             <span class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-2\" data-kid=\"304\">$3,500</span>\n             <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"305\">Средний старт</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"306\">\n             <span class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-2\" data-kid=\"307\">24/7</span>\n             <span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]\" data-kid=\"308\">Поддержка</span>\n          </div>\n       </div>\n       \n       <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center\" data-kid=\"309\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"px-12 py-5 bg-(--primary) text-black font-black rounded-sm uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-(--secondary) transition-all\" data-kid=\"310\">Записаться на курс</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"px-12 py-5 border border-white/20 text-white font-black rounded-sm uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all\" data-kid=\"311\">Смотреть демо</a>\n       </div>\n       \n       <p class=\"mt-12 text-white/30 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"312\">Доступ навсегда • Обновления бесплатно • Поддержка 24/7</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<footer class=\"py-20 border-t border-white/5\" data-kid=\"313\">\n   <div class=\"container mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"314\">\n      <div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-10 text-white/40 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\" data-kid=\"315\">\n         <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"316\">\n            <img src=\"/logo.svg\" alt=\"Logo\" class=\"h-6 opacity-50\" data-kid=\"317\">\n            <span data-kid=\"318\">&copy; 2026 DISPATCH4YOU ACADEMY</span>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"flex gap-10\" data-kid=\"319\">\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-(--primary) transition-colors\" data-kid=\"320\">Privacy Policy</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-(--primary) transition-colors\" data-kid=\"321\">Terms of Service</a>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-(--primary) transition-colors\" data-kid=\"322\">Contact</a>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"flex gap-6 text-xl\" data-kid=\"323\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-brand-instagram cursor-pointer hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"324\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-brand-facebook cursor-pointer hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"325\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-brand-youtube cursor-pointer hover:text-white transition-colors\" data-kid=\"326\"></i>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</footer>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"327\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"328\"></script>\n\n<script data-kid=\"329\">\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n  window.addEventListener('load', () => {\n    // Initial Reveal\n    gsap.from('.hero-reveal', {\n      opacity: 0,\n      y: 40,\n      duration: 1.2,\n      stagger: 0.2,\n      ease: 'power4.out',\n      delay: 0.5\n    });\n\n    // Scroll Reveals\n    gsap.utils.toArray('.reveal').forEach(el => {\n      gsap.from(el, {\n        scrollTrigger: {\n          trigger: el,\n          start: 'top 85%',\n          toggleActions: 'play none none none'\n        },\n        opacity: 0,\n        y: 60,\n        duration: 1,\n        ease: 'power3.out'\n      });\n    });\n\n    // Timeline Animation\n    gsap.to('#timeline-fill', {\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: '#how',\n        start: 'top center',\n        end: 'bottom center',\n        scrub: true\n      },\n      height: '100%',\n      ease: 'none'\n    });\n\n    // Timeline Nodes Highlight\n    gsap.utils.toArray('.timeline-node').forEach(node => {\n      gsap.from(node, {\n        scrollTrigger: {\n          trigger: node,\n          start: 'top center',\n          toggleActions: 'play reverse play reverse'\n        },\n        opacity: 0.2,\n        scale: 0.95,\n        duration: 0.5\n      });\n    });\n\n    // Counter Animation\n    gsap.utils.toArray('.counter').forEach(counter => {\n       const target = parseFloat(counter.dataset.target);\n       const suffix = counter.innerText.replace(/[0-9.]/g, '');\n       const prefix = counter.innerText.startsWith('$') ? '$' : '';\n       \n       gsap.to({ val: 0 }, {\n          val: target,\n          duration: 2,\n          scrollTrigger: {\n             trigger: counter,\n             start: 'top 90%'\n          },\n          onUpdate: function() {\n             counter.innerText = prefix + this.targets()[0].val.toFixed(target % 1 === 0 ? 0 : 1) + suffix;\n          }\n       });\n    });\n  });\n</script>",
